  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "crypto-system-assignment-apis",
    "name": "Crypto System - Full Flow",
    "description": "## Limit order test\nRun folder **2 - Limit order (1 order)** with Collection Runner.\n\nPlaces **one** ETH limit buy \u2192 checks **FILLED** (matched) \u2192 checks **ETH** in wallet.\n\nScheduler every 2s: fetch price, scan orders, fill, credit ETH. BUY matches when bestAsk <= limitPrice.",
